.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-PAY-AMOUNT-KURTOSIS-WEEKLY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-pay-amount-kurtosis-weekly \- FEAT-2844 node-pay-amount-kurtosis-weekly
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-pay-amount-kurtosis-weekly
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes the excess kurtosis of payment amounts (msat) for payments completed in the past week for the lightning CLI (FEAT-2844).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBamount_kurtosis_weekly\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
